:840313,"uid":121260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:41:38.000Z","msg":"我都係咁，report左比ea，佢基本就係要你關曬所有應用程式、防火牆、clean start部機、更新曬所以需要既驅動程式，但我都係唔得，你可以試下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T18:43:34.000Z","msg":"係咪呢封?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n你同我情況應該一樣  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先我对您遇到的问题表示歉意。從您的案子中我們發現您無法順利進行遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n為了解決您的問題，我需要您執行一些基本的修復教程步驟。<br />\n<br />\n1.確保主機桌面沒有開啟其它的應用程序。<br />\n2.確定殺毒軟件已關（因為該軟件會影響某些遊戲的接入）。<br />\n3.確定主機火墻系統已關（Windows Firewall）。<br />\n<br />\n如果以上步驟無法湊效，請執行以下的修復教程步驟。<br />\n<br />\n1.從<a href=\"https://www.piriform.com/ccleaner下載C清潔器（CCleaner）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.piriform.com%2Fccleaner%E4%B8%8B%E8%BC%89C%E6%B8%85%E6%BD%94%E5%99%A8%EF%BC%88CCleaner%EF%BC%89&d=LX%2BWfoYsR01hPJyzw8516p4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=bb1492d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.piriform.com/ccleaner下載C清潔器（CCleaner）</a><br />\n2.下載完畢後請啟動CCleaner.<br />\n3.根據以下網址所提供的步驟點擊有關訊息的框<br />\n<a href=\"http://help.ea.com/en/article/how-to-use-ccleaner-to-fix-pc-issues/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhelp.ea.com%2Fen%2Farticle%2Fhow-to-use-ccleaner-to-fix-pc-issues%2F&d=LX%2BWfoYsR01hPJyzw8516p4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=d9f4e3eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://help.ea.com/en/article/how-to-use-ccleaner-to-fix-pc-issues/</a><br />\n4.選擇完畢以後請點擊清潔運行（Run Cleaner）。<br />\n<br />\n另一個修復教程步驟是更新電腦系統。以下是更新電腦系統的步驟。<br />\n<br />\n1. 確保操作系統更新。下面的鏈接將提供您如何升級操作系統<br />\n<a href=\"http://windows.microsoft.com/zh-tw/windows/help/windows-update\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwindows.microsoft.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fwindows%2Fhelp%2Fwindows-update&d=LX%2BWfoYsR01hPJyzw8516p4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=db008c16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://windows.microsoft.com/zh-tw/windows/help/windows-update</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 確保 DirectX Redistributable是最新的版本。從此網頁可下載 DirectX Redistributable<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.microsoft.com/zh-tw/download/details.aspx?id=35\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.microsoft.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fdownload%2Fdetails.aspx%3Fid%3D35&d=LX%2BWfoYsR01hPJyzw8516p4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=5a4b18a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.microsoft.com/zh-tw/download/details.aspx?id=35</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 確保DirectX處於最新版本。以下是其步驟。<br />\n&bull; 開啟遊戲的安裝文件夾。<br />\n&bull; 點擊_installer文件。<br />\n&bull; 尋找DirectX文件並點擊。<br />\n&bull; 點擊redist。<br />\n&bull; 尋找DXSETUP並點擊運行。<br />\n<br />\n4. 確保Net Framework是最新版本。從此網頁可下載<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.microsoft.com/net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.microsoft.com%2Fnet&d=LX%2BWfoYsR01hPJyzw8516p4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=38c952ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.microsoft.com/net</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 更新Visual C++<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.microsoft.com/kb/2019667\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.microsoft.com%2Fkb%2F2019667&d=LX%2BWfoYsR01hPJyzw8516p4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=5bf95481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://support.microsoft.com/kb/2019667</a><br />\n<br />\n6. 更新顯示卡程序。以下的網頁提供您不同品牌的顯示卡官方網站<br />\n<a href=\"http://help.ea.com/en/article/finding-devices-and-updating-drivers/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhelp.ea.com%2Fen%2Farticle%2Ffinding-devices-and-updating-drivers%2F&d=LX%2BWfoYsR01hPJyzw8516p4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=5082b2d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://help.ea.com/en/article/finding-devices-and-updating-drivers/</a><br />\n<br />\n同時也提供您如何在Windows中執行初始狀態開機。<br />\n<br />\na) 在Start菜單中輸入&ldquo;msconfig&rdquo;後按enter。<br />\nb) 在System Configuration中選擇Services。<br />\nc) 點擊以選中&ldquo;Hide all Microsoft services&rdquo;後點擊&ldquo;Disable all&rdquo;按鍵。<br />\nd) 至Startup。<br />\ne) 點擊&ldquo;Disable all&rdquo;按鍵後點擊&ldquo;Apply&rdquo;<br />\n*有關如何在Windows中執行初始狀態開機的資訊請至（<a href=\"http://support.microsoft.com/kb/929135）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsupport.microsoft.com%2Fkb%2F929135%EF%BC%89&d=LX%2BWfoYsR01hPJyzw8516p4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=3b9082c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://support.microsoft.com/kb/929135）</a><br />\n<br />\n希望以上的修復教程步驟能讓您進入遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n如果您還面對著同樣的問題，請再次與我們聯繫。我們將非常樂意的為您提供進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n感謝您的耐心與理解。<br />\n<br />\n感謝聯繫EA客服。"},{"pid":"7ef164716fd3aa86fdcaa4d92c8b11e3af7292ee","tid":840313,"uid":121260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12a2be07566b4f137e249749d8983b1b650780ad","tid":840313,"uid":81497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"705f7c04aeaa26e8976596f115b384e06ae87cb1","tid":840313,"uid":121260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:41:38.000Z","msg":"我都係咁，report左比ea，佢基本就係要你關曬所有應用程式、防火牆、clean start部機、更新曬所以需要既驅動程式，但我都係唔得，你可以試下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T18:43:34.000Z","msg":"係咪呢封?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n你同我情況應該一樣  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先我对您遇到的问题表示歉意。從您的案子中我們發現您無法順利進行遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n為了解決您的問題，我需要您執行一些基本的修復教程步驟。<br />\n<br />\n1.確保主機桌面沒有開啟其它的應用程序。<br />\n2.確定殺毒軟件已關（因為該軟件會影響某些遊戲的接入）。<br />\n3.確定主機火墻系統已關（Windows Firewall）。<br />\n<br />\n如果以上步驟無法湊效，請執行以下的修復教程步驟。<br />\n<br />\n1.從<a href=\"https://www.piriform.com/ccleaner下載C清潔器（CCleaner）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.piriform.com%2Fccleaner%E4%B8%8B%E8%BC%89C%E6%B8%85%E6%BD%94%E5%99%A8%EF%BC%88CCleaner%EF%BC%89&d=LX%2BWfoYsR01hPJyzw8516p4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=bb1492d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.piriform.com/ccleaner下載C清潔器（CCleaner）</a><br />\n2.下載完畢後請啟動CCleaner.<br />\n3.根據以下網址所提供的步驟點擊有關訊息的框<br />\n<a href=\"http://help.ea.com/en/article/how-to-use-ccleaner-to-fix-pc-issues/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhelp.ea.com%2Fen%2Farticle%2Fhow-to-use-ccleaner-to-fix-pc-issues%2F&d